          <p data-i18n="hw.pEmu">An admin toggle puts every device adapter (conveyors, ASRS, AMR, AutoStore) into emulator mode: it simulates the machines and emits synthetic telemetry, so you can run the whole automation flow with zero hardware. Ideal for evaluation, onboarding, and CI.</p>
